  26 Mar 2004; Tom Payne <twp@gentoo.org> lua-5.0.2.ebuild :
  Marked stable on x86. Bug # 45739.

  26 Mar 2004; Tom Payne <twp@gentoo.org> lua-4.0.ebuild, lua-4.0.1.ebuild, lua-5.0.ebuild :
